title: Quirky font
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244im_/http:/typophile.com/files/planetuni_5422.png)

Can someone identify the fonts used in this image mainly the font for the words Planet & Uni but if possible the other words tooo please
author: chansena

comments.content:
Can't identify any of them.  
'planetUNI': you may like the work of [Rodrigo Araya Salas](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/foundry/RodrigoTypo)  
'the... ministry': I like [Cocobella](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/cultivated-mind/cocobella), [Toothpaste](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/search/toothpaste), [I'm Fashionista](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/fontscafe/im-fashionista), [Pastiche Brush](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/schizotype/pastiche-brush)  
'UNIVERSITY': [Supernett](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/facetype/supernett-cn), [D.I.Y. Time](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/latinotype/d-i-y-time), [Men In Black Credits](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.dafont.com/men-in-black-credits.font), [Amorie](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/kimmy/amorie), [The Hand](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/la-goupil/the-hand), [Italo](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/antipixel/italo), [Aracne](http://web.archive.org/web/20141028211244/http:/www.myfonts.com/search/aracne)
